sentences.english: An approach of grading fertile eggs based on computer vision was presented.
sentences.chinese: 提出一種利用計算機視覺對種蛋進行篩選的方法。

sentences.english: It suggested that Zinc can improved the breeding egg performance in colored pheasants.
sentences.chinese: 表明添加鋅有利於提高七彩山雞的種蛋性能。

sentences.english: All testing groups' fertility and hatchability were significantly higher than that of control group.
sentences.chinese: 各試驗組種蛋的受精率和孵化率均高於對照組。

sentences.english: Egg size can influence the future development of broilers.
sentences.chinese: 種蛋大小可影響肉雞發育。
